msgid ""
"So anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti, bahudhāpi "
"hutvā eko hoti; āvibhāvaṃ tirobhāvaṃ tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ "
"asajjamāno gacchati seyyathāpi ākāse; pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ karoti "
"seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāne gacchati seyyathāpi pathaviyā; ākāsepi "
"pallaṅkena kamati seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye "
"evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā parāmasati parimajjati; yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:88.6"
msgid ""
"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "dn2:88.7"
msgid "4.3.3.4. Dibbasotañāṇa"
msgstr ""

#. </h5><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs89"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc103"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:89.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte dibbāya sotadhātuyā cittaṃ "
"abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:89.2"
msgid ""
"So dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya atikkantamānusikāya ubho sadde suṇāti "
"dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike ca."
msgstr ""

# Compare AN 4.114: bheripaṇavasaṅkhatiṇavaninnādasaddānaṃ
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs90"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc104"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:90.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso addhānamaggappaṭipanno. So suṇeyya "
"bherisaddampi mudiṅgasaddampi saṅkhapaṇavadindimasaddampi. Tassa evamassa: "
"‘bherisaddo’ itipi, ‘mudiṅgasaddo’ itipi, ‘saṅkhapaṇavadindimasaddo’ itipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:90.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte "
"anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte dibbāya "
"sotadhātuyā cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:90.3"
msgid ""
"So dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya atikkantamānusikāya ubho sadde suṇāti "
"dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:90.4"
msgid ""
"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "dn2:90.5"
msgid "4.3.3.5. Cetopariyañāṇa"
msgstr ""

#. </h5><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs91"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.80"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc105"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:91.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte cetopariyañāṇāya cittaṃ abhinīharati "
"abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:91.2"
msgid ""
"So parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāti—sarāgaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘sarāgaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vītarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vītarāgaṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘sadosaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vītadosaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"‘vītadosaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, samohaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘samohaṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vītamohaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, saṅkhittaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘saṅkhittaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vikkhittaṃ "
"cittan’ti pajānāti, mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ ‘mahaggataṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, "
"amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ ‘amahaggataṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, sauttaraṃ vā cittaṃ ‘"
"sauttaraṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ ‘anuttaraṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘samāhitaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, asamāhitaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘asamāhitaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vimuttaṃ cittan’"
"ti pajānāti, avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘avimuttaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs92"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.81"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc106"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:92.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, itthī vā puriso vā daharo yuvā maṇḍanajātiko ādāse vā "
"parisuddhe pariyodāte acche vā udakapatte sakaṃ mukhanimittaṃ "
"paccavekkhamāno sakaṇikaṃ vā ‘sakaṇikan’ti jāneyya, akaṇikaṃ vā ‘akaṇikan’ti "
"jāneyya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:92.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte "
"anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte "
"cetopariyañāṇāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:92.3"
msgid ""
"So parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāti—sarāgaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘sarāgaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vītarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vītarāgaṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘sadosaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vītadosaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"‘vītadosaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, samohaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘samohaṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vītamohaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, saṅkhittaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘saṅkhittaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vikkhittaṃ "
"cittan’ti pajānāti, mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ ‘mahaggataṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, "
"amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ ‘amahaggataṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, sauttaraṃ vā cittaṃ ‘"
"sauttaraṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ ‘anuttaraṃ cittan’ti "
"pajānāti, samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘samāhitaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, asamāhitaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ ‘asamāhitaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti, vimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘vimuttaṃ cittan’"
"ti pajānāti, avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘avimuttaṃ cittan’ti pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:92.4"
msgid ""
"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "dn2:92.5"
msgid "4.3.3.6. Pubbe­nivāsā­nus­sati­ñāṇa"
msgstr ""

#. </h5><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs93"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc107"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:93.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:93.2"
msgid ""
"So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi "
"jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi "
"jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi "
"jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe, ‘amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo "
"evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra "
"udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti. "
"Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs94"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.82"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc108"></a>
#. VAR: agacchiṃ → agañchiṃ (s1-3, km) | agañciṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "dn2:94.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso sakamhā gāmā aññaṃ gāmaṃ gaccheyya, tamhāpi "
"gāmā aññaṃ gāmaṃ gaccheyya. So tamhā gāmā sakaṃyeva gāmaṃ paccāgaccheyya. "
"Tassa evamassa: ‘ahaṃ kho sakamhā gāmā amuṃ gāmaṃ agacchiṃ, tatra evaṃ "
"aṭṭhāsiṃ, evaṃ nisīdiṃ, evaṃ abhāsiṃ, evaṃ tuṇhī ahosiṃ, tamhāpi gāmā amuṃ "
"gāmaṃ agacchiṃ, tatrāpi evaṃ aṭṭhāsiṃ, evaṃ nisīdiṃ, evaṃ abhāsiṃ, evaṃ "
"tuṇhī ahosiṃ, somhi tamhā gāmā sakaṃyeva gāmaṃ paccāgato’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:94.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte "
"anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte "
"pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:94.3"
msgid ""
"So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi "
"jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi "
"jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi "
"jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe, ‘amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo "
"evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra "
"udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro "
"evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti. "
"Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:94.4"
msgid ""
"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "dn2:94.5"
msgid "4.3.3.7. Dibba­cak­khu­ñāṇa"
msgstr ""

#. </h5><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs95"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.83"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc109"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:95.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte sattānaṃ cutūpapātañāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:95.2"
msgid ""
"So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne "
"upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate, yathākammūpage "
"satte pajānāti: ‘ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā "
"vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā "
"micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā. Te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā. Ime vā pana bhonto sattā "
"kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena "
"samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ti. Iti dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne "
"hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate, yathākammūpage satte pajānāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc110"></a>
#. VAR: rathikāyapi vīthiṃ sañcarante → rathiyā vīti­sañ­caran­tenapi (bj) | rathiyāya vithiṃ sañcarantepi (s1-3) | rathiyā vīthi sañcarantepi (pts1)
msgctxt "dn2:96.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, majjhe siṅghāṭake pāsādo. Tattha cakkhumā puriso ṭhito "
"passeyya manusse gehaṃ pavisantepi nikkhamantepi rathikāyapi vīthiṃ "
"sañcarante majjhe siṅghāṭake nisinnepi. Tassa evamassa: ‘ete manussā gehaṃ "
"pavisanti, ete nikkhamanti, ete rathikāya vīthiṃ sañcaranti, ete majjhe "
"siṅghāṭake nisinnā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:96.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte "
"anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte sattānaṃ "
"cutūpapātañāṇāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:96.3"
msgid ""
"So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne "
"upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate, yathākammūpage "
"satte pajānāti: ‘ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā "
"vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā "
"micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā. Ime vā pana bhonto sattā "
"kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena "
"samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā. Te "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ti. Iti dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne "
"hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate; yathākammūpage satte pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:96.4"
msgid ""
"Idampi kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "dn2:96.5"
msgid "4.3.3.8. Āsa­vak­kha­ya­ñāṇa"
msgstr ""

#. </h5><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs97"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.84"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc111"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:97.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte āsavānaṃ khayañāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:97.2"
msgid ""
"So idaṃ dukkhanti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ayaṃ dukkhasamudayoti yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ayaṃ dukkhanirodhoti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadāti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:97.3"
msgid ""
"Ime āsavāti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ayaṃ āsavasamudayoti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, "
"ayaṃ āsavanirodhoti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ayaṃ āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadāti "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:97.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, bhavāsavāpi "
"cittaṃ vimuccati, avijjāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:97.5"
msgid "vimuttasmiṃ ‘vimuttam’iti ñāṇaṃ hoti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:97.6"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs98"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.85"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc112"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:98.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, pabbatasaṅkhepe udakarahado accho vippasanno anāvilo. "
"Tattha cakkhumā puriso tīre ṭhito passeyya sippisambukampi "
"sakkharakathalampi macchagumbampi carantampi tiṭṭhantampi. Tassa evamassa: ‘"
"ayaṃ kho udakarahado accho vippasanno anāvilo. Tatrime sippisambukāpi "
"sakkharakathalāpi macchagumbāpi carantipi tiṭṭhantipī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, mahārāja, bhikkhu evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte "
"anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte āsavānaṃ "
"khayañāṇāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.3"
msgid ""
"‘So idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.4"
msgid ""
"‘Ime āsavā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ āsavanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ "
"āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, bhavāsavāpi "
"cittaṃ vimuccati, avijjāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.6"
msgid "vimuttasmiṃ ‘vimuttam’iti ñāṇaṃ hoti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.7"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.8"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ kho, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikaṃ sāmaññaphalaṃ purimehi sandiṭṭhikehi "
"sāmaññaphalehi abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:98.9"
msgid ""
"Imasmā ca pana, mahārāja, sandiṭṭhikā sāmaññaphalā aññaṃ sandiṭṭhikaṃ "
"sāmaññaphalaṃ uttaritaraṃ vā paṇītataraṃ vā natthī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn2:98.10"
msgid "5. Ajātasattuupāsakattapaṭivedanā"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs99"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc113"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:99.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rājā māgadho ajātasattu vedehiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, "
"mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya: ‘"
"cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.4"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.5"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gataṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.6"
msgid ""
"Accayo maṃ, bhante, accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, yohaṃ "
"pitaraṃ dhammikaṃ dhammarājānaṃ issariyakāraṇā jīvitā voropesiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:99.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa me, bhante bhagavā, accayaṃ accayato paṭiggaṇhātu āyatiṃ saṃvarāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs100"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc114"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:100.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha tvaṃ, mahārāja, accayo accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ "
"yathāakusalaṃ, yaṃ tvaṃ pitaraṃ dhammikaṃ dhammarājānaṃ jīvitā voropesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:100.2"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho tvaṃ, mahārāja, accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ paṭikarosi, "
"taṃ te mayaṃ paṭiggaṇhāma."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:100.3"
msgid ""
"Vuddhihesā, mahārāja, ariyassa vinaye, yo accayaṃ accayato disvā "
"yathādhammaṃ paṭikaroti, āyatiṃ saṃvaraṃ āpajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs101"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc115"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:101.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rājā māgadho ajātasattu vedehiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:101.2"
msgid "“handa ca dāni mayaṃ, bhante, gacchāma bahukiccā mayaṃ bahukaraṇīyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:101.3"
msgid "“Yassadāni tvaṃ, mahārāja, kālaṃ maññasī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:101.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā māgadho ajātasattu vedehiputto bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā "
"anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs102"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.86"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc116"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:102.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā acirapakkantassa rañño māgadhassa ajātasattussa "
"vedehiputtassa bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""

# Note that these terms are commonly used in the context of keeping sila, eg AN 3.50 etc.
msgctxt "dn2:102.2"
msgid "“khatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:102.3"
msgid "Upahatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:102.4"
msgid ""
"Sacāyaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā pitaraṃ dhammikaṃ dhammarājānaṃ jīvitā na "
"voropessatha, imasmiññeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ "
"uppajjissathā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc117"></a>
msgctxt "dn2:102.5"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn2:102.6"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn2:102.7"
msgid "Sāmaññaphalasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
